EXTRACTED VALUE: A laugh-out-loud, gun toting riot of action. [Nov 2006, p.67]
Never has picking up rubbish felt so good. [Jan 2008, p.92]
This is, in all possibility, the most stunningly attractive game the PlayStation has ever known.
If you are of the old school class that enjoys the simple things in life you will undoubtedly find a lot to like about this game.
